com.apriori.di

Interface AbstractBinding.BindBuilder<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of value being bound
    All Superinterfaces:
    AbstractBinding.ScopeBuilder<T>
    Enclosing class:
    AbstractBinding

    public static interface AbstractBinding.BindBuilder<T>
extends AbstractBinding.ScopeBuilder<T>
    A builder for bindings. This is used to create bindings with APIs that are easier to read and write than always constructing raw Keys.
